window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Tom Mison, star of the hit Fox series <i>Sleepy Hollow</i>, narrates the classic Washington Irving short story. </p> <p>In the secluded Dutch territory of Sleepy Hollow, nebbish schoolmaster Ichabod Crane competes with the town hero for the hand of Katrina Van Tassel, the 18-year-old daughter and sole child of a wealthy farmer. As Crane leaves a party at the Van Tassel's farm one autumn evening, he is pursued by the Headless Horseman, an apparition said to be the ghost of a Hessian trooper snuffed out by a stray cannonball during the Revolutionary War.</p>"; 
